seg.source: 西藏尼玛县连发4.4、4.5级地震暂未造成人员伤亡
seg.translation: Consecutive earthquakes registering 4.4 and 4.5 on the Richter scale has occurred at the Tibetan County of Nima, no has been hurt or killed
No casualties caused by 4.4 and 4.5 earthquake in Nima County, Tibet
No casualties caused by successive earthquakes of magnitude 4.4 and 4.5 in Nima County, Tibet

seg.source: 据地方民政部门报告，目前暂未造成人员伤亡，具体灾情正在进一步统计核查中。
seg.translation: Local civil affairs departments reported that no casualty has been caused. The severity and damages caused by the disaster is currently being calculated and verified.
According to the local civil affairs Department reported that there is no casualties, the specific disaster is further statistical verification.
